\nw[Receptionist]This is the government office. Please feel free to
ask if you need anything. (Please don't say
anything that will give me more work.)

\nw[Staff]Hmmm, there seems to be an issue with flood
control...

\nw[Staff]It seems that there are many monsters in the
vicinity of this town after all. However, with
this budget, relying on mercenaries seems to be
the only option...

\nw[Staff]Even though it's an entertainment city, we should
improve the public order a little more...

\nw[Staff]*sigh*... I'm tired from work all the time. This
is the perfect time to be healed by a songstress.
